headline: AbbVie Awards 20 Individuals Living With Migraine To Support Career Aspirations
summary: AbbVie (NYSE: ABBV) today announced 20 winners of the inaugural AbbVie Migraine Career Catalyst Award™ contest, a first-of-its-kind contest designed to support the career aspirations of people living with migraine. The winning entries were selected from short essay, video, and audio clip submissions highlighting entrants' experiences living with migraine, their career aspirations, and how this award could help support their future success.
